{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "bachhoammo-seller-api",
    "name": "BachHoaMMO Seller API",
    "description": "# BachHoaMMO Seller API\n\nAPI cho seller quản lý kho hàng, sản phẩm và đơn hàng trên BachHoaMMO.\n\n## Authentication\n\nMỗi request cần 3 headers:\n- `X-API-Key`: API Key của bạn (bắt đầu bằng `bhmmo_`)\n- `X-Timestamp`: Unix timestamp (giây)\n- `X-Signature`: HMAC-SHA256 signature\n\n### Tính signature\n\n```javascript\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\n\nconst signaturePayload = timestamp + method + path + body;\nconst signature = crypto\n  .createHmac('sha256', secretHash)\n  .update(signaturePayload)\n  .digest('hex');\n```\n\n## Rate Limits\n\n- Default: 100 requests/phút\n- Headers trả về: `X-RateLimit-Limit`, `X-RateLimit-Remaining`, `X-RateLimit-Reset`\n\n## Error Response\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"ERROR_CODE\",\n    \"message\": \"Error description\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Support\n\n- Website: https://bachhoammo.store\n- Email: support@bachhoammo.store",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "https://bachhoammo.store",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_key",
      "value": "bhmmo_your_api_key_here",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_secret",
      "value": "your_secret_here",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// BachHoaMMO API - Auto-generate signature",
          "const timestamp = Math.floor(Date.now() / 1000).toString();",
          "const method = pm.request.method.toUpperCase();",
          "const path = pm.request.url.getPath();",
          "",
          "// Get body and minify (remove whitespace/newlines to match server)",
          "let body = '';",
          "if (pm.request.body && pm.request.body.raw) {",
          "    try {",
          "        const parsed = JSON.parse(pm.request.body.raw);",
          "        body = JSON.stringify(parsed);",
          "    } catch (e) {",
          "        body = pm.request.body.raw;",
          "    }",
          "}",
          "",
          "// Get API secret from collection variables",
          "const secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('api_secret') || pm.variables.get('api_secret');",
          "",
          "// Create signature payload: timestamp + method + path + body",
          "const signaturePayload = timestamp + method + path + body;",
          "",
          "// Generate HMAC-SHA256 signature",
          "const signature = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(signaturePayload, secret).toString();",
          "",
          "// Debug log (check in Postman Console)",
          "console.log('=== Signature Debug ===');",
          "console.log('Timestamp:', timestamp);",
          "console.log('Method:', method);",
          "console.log('Path:', path);",
          "console.log('Body:', body);",
          "console.log('Payload:', signaturePayload);",
          "console.log('Signature:', signature);",
          "",
          "// Set headers",
          "pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'X-API-Key', value: pm.collectionVariables.get('api_key') || pm.variables.get('api_key') });",
          "pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'X-Timestamp', value: timestamp });",
          "pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'X-Signature', value: signature });",
          "pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'Content-Type', value: 'application/json' });"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
